OL,6,FAt Old Delhi's busy, chaotic railway
OL,7,Fstation we are searching for lost
OL,8,Fchildren.
OL,10,FThe hundreds of trains coming in and
OL,11,Fgoing out don't just bring workers,
OL,12,Ffamilies and travellers - but
OL,13,Fvulnerable children too.
OL,15,FCharities estimate that in India a
OL,16,Fchild goes missing every 8 minutes -
OL,17,Fand the railways are the focus of
OL,18,Fefforts to find them.
OL,20,FI went to Delhi to investigate why
OL,21,Ffor ITV's On Assignment Programme.
OL,3,CLost on the railways - India's
OL,4,Cmissing children
